# NOTE: `.env` is intentionally NOT ignored — the production Vite build reads its
# VITE_* (public browser config, not secrets) at build time. Only the final nginx
# stage is shipped, and it copies just `dist/`, so `.env` is not in the runtime image.
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
npm-debug.log*
